net.sf.libai.fuzzy.sets
Class Trapezoid

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.libai.fuzzy.sets.Trapezoid
All Implemented Interfaces:
FuzzySet
public class Trapezoid
extends java.lang.Object
implements FuzzySet

Fuzzy set representing a trapezoid function. The trapezoid function can take 3 variations:

  • right trapezoid to the left. a = b != c != d.
  • centered trapezoid a != b != c != d.
  • right trapezoid to the right a != b != c = d.
In the three cases, the support of the set is the interval [a,d].
The kernel is always the interval [b,c].
